query:
UPDATE products 
SET categoryId = 8 
WHERE name LIKE '%Guardian%' 
   OR name LIKE '%Blessed%' 
   OR name LIKE '%Bracelet%' 
   OR name LIKE '%Pendant%' 
   OR name LIKE '%Zodiac%';
